This is the textbook for the ELEC 3040/3050 (Embedded Systems Design
Lab) class.
 
Students are expected to have at least been introduced to the concepts
in this book in ELEC 2220 (Computer Systems) before reading this book.
 
No generative AI (ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude, etc) was used in the
production of this book.
 
Thank you Dr. Brown, Dr. Nelson, and Dr. Nelms for their feedback during the composition of this book!
:enotices.
:vnotice.
