primer,:eq. this book is :hp1.heavily:ehp1. targeted towards being a 
reference that is easily flipped through! Use the retrieval key at the 
top of each page, or the subject at the bottom  right of every page to 
find things quickly!
:coprnote.&copr. Evie Cooper 2026
