:c.:pk.char:epk.
:c.8-bit ASCII character
:c.:hdref refid=vars.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.short:epk.
:c.16-bit small integer
:c.:hdref refid=vars.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.long:epk.
:c.32-bit integer (:pv.long:epv.s are 32 bits wide on 32-bit CPUs)
:c.:hdref refid=vars.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.float:epk.
:c.Single-precision floating-point number
:c.:hdref refid=vars.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.double:epk.
:c.Double-precision floating-point number
:c.:hdref refid=vars.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.void:epk.
:c.Lack of a type (only for functions and some pointers)
:c.:hdref refid=funcs.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.signed:epk.
:c.Store the value with 2's complement
:c.:hdref refid=vars.
