:ethd.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.const:epk.
:c.Make a variable a constant
:c.:hdref refid=quals.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.volatile:epk.
:c.Disable optimization for a variable; inform the compiler that
the variable's value may change at any time
:c.:hdref refid=quals.
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.restrict:epk.
:c.Mark a pointer as being the only read/write path to the variable
it points to (the variable itself on the other side of the pointer
will only be accessed through this pointer)
