:etable.
:p.You will use this value later when you alter the sequence selection 
with the :pk.ADC1->SQR1:epk. register!
:h3.The ADC Configuration Registers
:p.We will need alter at least three registers in order to configure 
our ADC; we will use :pk.ADC1:epk. for our experiments.
:p.Check the :hp1.RM0394 Reference Manual:ehp1. (see 
:hdref refid=biblio. for this document) to see the layout of:
:ol.
:li.:pk.ADC_CR:epk.
:li.:pk.ADC_CFGR:epk.
:li.:pk.ADC_SQR1:epk. 
:eol.
:p.Here they are for the STM32L432KCU for your viewing convinence: 
